data.description: Introducing a picture-perfect newer construction home nestled in the charming Covington neighborhood, Orchard Park. Minutes from Historical Downtown Covington and the new Covington Town Center, and just steps to the 3-Ring Studios, this home is in a prime location.  Meticulously cared for and beautifully designed, this home has one of the largest floor plans in the community.  Upon arrival, you will be greeted to stunning curb appeal and a darling front porch. Inside, enjoy a traditional entry with a foyer and large dining room, leading to an open concept kitchen and living room.  A true entertainer's dream with multiple dining areas, a spacious footprint, and a walk-out backyard with covered porch and privacy fence. Upstairs, find four spacious bedrooms- each with vaulted ceilings and large closets, a guest bathroom with dual vanity, laundry room, and more storage space.  The incredible primary suite offers a seating area, two grand walk-in closets, and an updated primary bathroom with dual sinks, a soaking tub with frosted picture window, and a glass shower. Additional details include beautiful hardwood flooring throughout the main level, new light fixtures, fresh paint, and pre-wiring for an electric car.  Orchard Park is known for its amazing amenities, including a pool, tennis courts, pond, green space, gazebo, and more.  Imagine life at 90 Orchard Lane. **NEW BUYER INCENTIVE: $4,000 towards Buyer's closing costs if using preferred lender.**
